    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――大会当日",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ついに本番だよ、後輩君……！\n衣装も似合ってるし、完璧だよ！",
      "startTime": 6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "素敵な世紀末アイドルになれてる！\n今までの練習の成果、全力で披露してきてね！",
      "startTime": 12.1333325069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。最初はツンツンな髪形も、トゲトゲが付いた\nベストも、マスクも、不審者過ぎると思っていたが……",
      "startTime": 20.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣のおかげで、アイドルの特訓を積んだ今なら\nとても体に馴染んでいる気がするよ",
      "startTime": 27.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、うんうん！　すっごく似合ってるよー！\n面白くて、ずっと笑顔になっちゃうもん",
      "startTime": 35.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-suzukiana001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が笑ってくれる……凄いな、それだけで\n力が溢れてくるようだ。これが、アイドル……！",
      "startTime": 42.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8400.005380299994,
          "startTime": 46.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5033.3333333,
          "startTime": 47.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "リングアナウンサー鈴木",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "仕上がってますね、{user}さん……",
      "startTime": 47.2999946197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "リングアナウンサー鈴木",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いや、我が相棒、まきびし丸！",
      "startTime": 50.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、確かに髪形が、まきびしみたいだよね！\nすっごくぴったりでカッコいいよ！",
      "startTime": 58.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "リングアナウンサー鈴木",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-suzukiana002.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、そろそろ初陣ですよ！　世紀末パンク\nラップアイドル『まきびし丸 with スズキ』の！",
      "startTime": 65.8666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣もそろそろ準備しなきゃだ！\nお互い、頑張ろうね！　まきびし丸！",
      "startTime": 72.6333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ！　もし戦うことになってもよぉ……\n手加減はなしだぜぇ！　ひーはー！！",
      "startTime": 80.8000017802,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5499.996947299991,
          "startTime": 86.2999987275
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（――その後、初戦で芽衣達と当たり）\n（俺と鈴木さんは無事、電流爆破された）",
      "startTime": 89.9666684468,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_electricexplosion-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.336424999993,
          "startTime": 91.5666684468
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（芽衣達は順調に勝ち進んで決勝戦か……）\n（対戦相手は『BEIJU』……お、おばあちゃん？）",
      "startTime": 97.9333335876,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.666157999993,
          "startTime": 103.1999997456
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_prowrestlingring-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（なんてことだ……俺もアイドルの端くれだから分かる）\n（あれは、歴戦の猛者だ。芽衣達、勝てるのか……！？）",
      "startTime": 107.0999997456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "可愛いおばあちゃん達が相手だなんて、嬉しいなぁ～！\nやっぱり大会に出て良かったよー！",
      "startTime": 117.8666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "人生の先輩相手に、どこまで出来るか分かんないけど\nばぁば達も見ててね！",
      "startTime": 125.6666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "メイメイ達のパフォーマンスで、もっと元気になって\n一緒にすっごーいライブバトルにしようね！",
      "startTime": 131.6000017802,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6533.332824699997,
          "startTime": 134.3666684468
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い……俺はすっかり萎縮してしまっていたが）\n（芽衣達はいつも以上の輝きを見せてくれている）",
      "startTime": 140.0000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（どんな場所でも堂々と、観ている人達のために）\n（歌い、踊る。早坂芽衣は、本当に『アイドル』だな）",
      "startTime": 147.2666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 153.7333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（あの後、芽衣達は惜しくも決勝で敗退――）\n（さらには沙季に見つかり、寮へと連れ戻されていった）",
      "startTime": 159.8000017802,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4699.9944051,
          "startTime": 164.4999961853
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ～、{user}さん\n沙季ちゃんにすっごく怒られちゃったよ～",
      "startTime": 167.0000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "俺もだよ。あの後、芽衣達のフォローをしようと\nこっそり大会に出ていたことを話したんだが……",
      "startTime": 174.2333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "「いい大人が何をしてるんですか」とか「まきびし丸\nってなんなんですか」って、しこたま怒られたよ……",
      "startTime": 181.7000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "世紀末パンクアイドルでしょ？\nすっごーくかっこ良かったけどな～、まきびし丸！",
      "startTime": 187.9333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "や、やめてくれ、黒歴史になってるんだ……\nあの会場の熱にあてられてどうかしてたよ",
      "startTime": 195.1333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_14_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "でもその熱、悪くなかったでしょ？\n芽衣の言った通り、刺激的で楽しかったよね",
      "startTime": 201.8333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
